metadata.name: Alien Frenemies #1
metadata.description: Alien Frenemies is a community driven collection of 5555 NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain randomly generated from carefully curated traits. We are an intergalactic militia of rebellious, anti-social aliens that find common ground in being isolated, introverted, and an enemy of the fake-smiling, synthetic-laughing, sweet-talking society of 'frens' in the Metaverse.
